.DT
set_always_use_default_position
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_always_use_default_position

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_always_use_default_position -  This method sets the always the flag to always use the default position.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_always_use_default_position(int flag)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^flag%^RESET%^ - if we should always use the default position
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/living.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the always the flag to always use the default position.
If this is set then rooms cannot override the position message which is
displayed by the object.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
query_always_use_default_position(), set_default_position(), return_to_default_position()

.EP

